01_PROJECT OVERVIEW:

What is TALK-AI-TIVE?
TALK-AI-TIVE is a full-stack, AI-powered web application that lets users speak to their browser and get intelligent responses about any webpage. Users paste a URL, click a microphone button, speak a command вҖ” and the AI responds out loud.

The Core Idea in One Line
"Paste a URL вҶ’ Click Mic вҶ’ Speak вҶ’ AI responds out loud."

Who Is It Built For?
User: 
 How It Helps Them
Blind / Visually Impaired	: Hear webpage content without reading
Elderly Users	: Simplify complex websites with voice
Motor-Impaired Users  : navigate hands-free
Busy Students & Professionals : Summarize long pages instantly
Non-native Language Speakers : Translate & simplify content


